Mark your calendars — here's the schedule for the nightly "Light of Hope" shows, where colors of UAAP schools will light up the facade of the UST Main Building alongside their chants and hymns.

The light displays, which serve as a countdown to the UAAP Season 88 opening rites, celebrate the Jubilee of Hope and the University's mission to spread the light (lumina pandit).

(Art by Aidan Raphael F. Caluyo/ The Varsitarian)
